nt-mono tracking-widest text-zinc-800 uppercase font-bold">MICHELIN</span><span class="jsx-cbeda58747eddfe9 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-wider text-zinc-400 uppercase">(<!-- -->Premium Tires<!-- -->)</span></div><div class="jsx-cbeda58747eddfe9 inline-flex items-center gap-2.5"><div class="jsx-cbeda58747eddfe9 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></div><span class="jsx-cbeda58747eddfe9 text-xs font-mono tracking-widest text-zinc-800 uppercase font-bold">3M</span><span class="jsx-cbeda58747eddfe9 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-wider text-zinc-400 uppercase">(<!-- -->Car Care<!-- -->)</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="about" class="relative bg-[#f4f4f3] py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden border-b border-zinc-200"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(0,0,0,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(0,0,0,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)] opacity-100"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 relative z-10"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center" style="opacity:0"><div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6 text-left" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div><span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-orange-500 uppercase">WHO WE ARE</span><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-zinc-950 tracking-tight mt-2 uppercase leading-none">PRECISION SERVICE.<br/>EVERY TIME.</h2></div><p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">At Sangat Motor Centre, we combine advanced automotive technology with decades of skilled expertise to keep your high-performance vehicle running at its absolute best. We treat every car with a level of attention and precision that sets the benchmark in premium car maintenance.</p><p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-mono">EST. 2012 • 10,000+ VEHICLES DETAILED &amp; SERVICED</p><div class="pt-2"><a href="#services" class="inline-flex i